{"lemma": "عَلاقَةٌ", "slug": "عَلاقَةٌ", "root": "ع.ل.ق", "root_slug": "ع-ل-ق", "root_link": "/words/roots/ع-ل-ق", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 2, "pos_tags": ["noun"], "has_etymology": false, "sense_count": 6}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n30295", "n30296", "n30301"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "connection", "fa": "ارتباط", "ur": "تعلق", "tr": "bağlantı", "id": "hubungan", "bn": "সম্পর্ক", "es": "conexión", "fr": "lien", "de": "Verbindung", "ru": "связь", "zh": "联系"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "noun", "gloss": "verbal noun of عَلِقَ (ʕaliqa) (form I)", "tags": ["form-of", "noun-from-verb"]}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "relationship, kinship"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "relationship, connection"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "relation"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "relevance"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "coat hanger", "tags": ["rhetoric"]}]}, "etymology": null, "ipa": ["/ʕa.laː.qa/", "/ʕal.laː.qa/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n30295", "headword_ar": "عَلَاقَةٌ", "root": "Elq", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "[is originally an inf. n.: and as a simple subst. signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An attachment, a tie,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a connection;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuloqapN", "text_ar": "عُلْقَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", mentioned in the TA, in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rbT", "text_ar": "ربط"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", together with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wuSolapN", "text_ar": "وُصْلَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raAbiTapN", "text_ar": "رَابِطَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":] a word relating to things conceived in the mind; as love, and contention in an altercation: ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EilaAqapN", "text_ar": "عِلَاقَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "relating to things extrinsic to the mind; as a bow, and a whip: (Kull p. 262:) see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaqN", "text_ar": "عَلَقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", last quarter. ―         -b2-  [Hence, as denoting an attachment, or a tie,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Love,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "friendship;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as is true,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sincere;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hub~N", "text_ar": "حُبٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SadaAqapN", "text_ar": "صَدَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K, TA:) [or as expl. voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaqN", "text_ar": "عَلَقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", last quarter:] or it means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqapu Hub~K", "text_ar": "عَلَاقَةُ حُبٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an attachment,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a tie,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a clinging, of love"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S, O:) Lh mentions, on the authority of Ks, and as known to As, the saying"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahaA fiY", "text_ar": "لَهَا فِى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qalobiY EalaAqapu Hub~K", "text_ar": "قَلْبِى عَلَاقَةُ حُبٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There is to her, in my heart, an attachment,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a tie,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a clinging, of love"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; and likewise, on the authority of the former, but as unknown to As,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hub~K", "text_ar": "حُبٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eiloqu", "text_ar": "عِلْقُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hub~K", "text_ar": "حُبٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EilaAqapu", "text_ar": "عِلَاقَةُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", though As knew the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hub~K", "text_ar": "حُبٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ealaqu", "text_ar": "عَلَقُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqapu Hub~K", "text_ar": "عَلَاقَةُ حُبٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "love to which one clings."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A contention in an altercation; a dispute;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a litigation:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K: [see also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaqN", "text_ar": "عَلَقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", near the end of the paragraph:]) or it means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqapu xuSuwmapK", "text_ar": "عَلَاقَةُ خُصُومَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[app. one's"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "connection in such a contention"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S, O:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqapu xuSuwmapK", "text_ar": "عَلَاقَةُ خُصُومَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the proportion"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "share"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that one holds"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in such a contention;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what pertains to one thereof;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "one's concern therein"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (Msb:) [for] ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqapN", "text_ar": "عَلَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing upon which one has,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "retains, a hold;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuloqapN", "text_ar": "عُلْقَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the saying"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kul~u", "text_ar": "كُلُّ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayoEK A^aboqaY EuloqapF fahuwa biATilN", "text_ar": "بَيْعٍ اَبْقَى عُلْقَةً فَهُوَ بِاطِلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Every sale that leaves remaining"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a thing upon which the seller retains a hold"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is null"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Msb.) And one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA bayonahumaA EalaAqapN", "text_ar": "مَا بَيْنَهُمَا عَلَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", with fet-h, meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There is not between them two anything upon which either of them has a hold against the other:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and the pl. is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAy^iqu", "text_ar": "عَلَايِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lifulaAnK fiY h`*aA Ald~aAri EalaAqapN", "text_ar": "لِفُلَانٍ فِى هٰذَا الدَّارِ عَلَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [or rather"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*ihi AldAr", "text_ar": "هٰذِهِ الدار"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",] with fet-h, i. e. ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There belongs to such a one, in this house, something upon which he has a hold,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in which he has a concern,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a remaining portion of a share."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEalaAqapu mina Almahori", "text_ar": "العَلَاقَةُ مِنَ المَهْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "That"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "portion,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "amount, of the dowry,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "nuptial gift,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon which they have a hold against him who takes a woman in marriage:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Sh, K, TA:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAy^iqu", "text_ar": "عَلَايِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as above]: (K, TA:) whence the saying, in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ad~uwA AlEalaAy^iqa", "text_ar": "اَدُّوا العَلَايِقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e., as expl. by the Prophet, ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Pay ye"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what their families have agreed upon;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what attack each one of them"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by an obligation"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to his companion,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fellow, like as a thing is attached to another thing."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And [the pl.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAy^iqu", "text_ar": "عَلَايِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "likewise signifies ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Obligations of bloodwits;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bloodwits that are attached to a man."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) [See also another explanation in the fourth of the sentences here following.] ―         -b5-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A work, craft, trade,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "any other thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "occupation"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to which a man has attached himself:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a work"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "craft"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. as above, or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "property"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a wife"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a child,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "love,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a contention in an altercation, pertaining to a man"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yataEal~aqu biA_inosaAnK", "text_ar": "يَتَعَلَّقُ بِاـِنْسَانٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "): pl. as above. (Har p. 372.) ―         -b6-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuloqapN", "text_ar": "عُلْقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in three places. ―         -b7-  [The pl.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAy^iqu", "text_ar": "عَلَايِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is also expl. by Lh as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Articles of merchandise."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b8-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEalaAqapu", "text_ar": "العَلَاقَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is said by Sh to signify"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alnabolu", "text_ar": "النَبْلُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[evidently, I think, a mistranscription for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alt~abolu", "text_ar": "التَّبْلُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Blood-revenge;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the seeking for blood-revenge,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "though it seems to be better rendered"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the obligation of bloodrevenge;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the obligation of a bloodwit, attaching to a man,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "agreeably with an explanation given above]: and by Aboo-Nasr to signify"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alt~abaAEudu", "text_ar": "التَّبَاعُدُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[which I think to be a mistranscription for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alt~anaAfudu", "text_ar": "التَّنَافُدُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", signifying"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contention, disputation,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "litigation,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a meaning mentioned in the former half of this paragraph]: and both of these significations are assigned to it in the saying of Imra-el-Keys,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "biA^aY~i EalaAqatinaA tarogabuw\n                      \n                     \n                        na Eano dami EamorKw EalaY marovadi"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as though meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "By reason of what bloodrevenge,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of ours do ye relinquish the claim for the blood of 'Amr resting as a debt upon Marthad?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "What is our contention,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.?"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Do ye relinquish"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]: the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "b", "text_ar": "ب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[in"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biA^aY~i", "text_ar": "بِاَىِّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] accord. to the latter explanation being redundant. (TA. [See also De Slane's “ Diwan d'Amro'lkais, ” p. 48, line 4, of the Ar. text. (in which the former hemistich ends with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "trgbwn", "text_ar": "ترغبون"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and the latter commences with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aEano", "text_ar": "اَعَنْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "); and see his translation; and a gloss in the notes, p. 126.])       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaliyqapN", "text_ar": "عَلِيقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["K", "TA", "S", "O", "Msb", "Sh"]}, {"entry_id": "n30296", "headword_ar": "عِلَاقَةٌ", "root": "Elq", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaqN", "text_ar": "عَلَقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", last quarter; and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqapN", "text_ar": "عَلَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", first and second sentences. It signifies The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "suspensory thong"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of the knife and of other things; (Msb;) it is of the bow, (S, O, [see also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muEal~aqN", "text_ar": "مُعَلَّقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",]) and of the whip (S, Mgh, K) and the like, (K, TA,) as the sword, and the shield, and the drinking-cup or bowl, and of the book, or copy of the Kur-án, &c., (TA,) and of the water-skin; (M voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$inaAqN", "text_ar": "شِنَاقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";) that of the whip being the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thong that is in the handle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "thereof. (TA.) See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "miEolaAqN", "text_ar": "مِعْلَاقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". [Also The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "suspensory stalk"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a fruit.] ―         -b2-  And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A surname,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by-name;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "because it is attached to a man; as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAqiyapN", "text_ar": "عَلَاقِيَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", of which the pl. is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EulaAqaY", "text_ar": "عُلَاقَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": the pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EilaAqapN", "text_ar": "عِلَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaAy^iqu", "text_ar": "عَلَايِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "K", "TA"]}, {"entry_id": "n30301", "headword_ar": "عَلَّاقَةٌ", "root": "Elq", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaluwqN", "text_ar": "عَلُوقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", second sentence."}], "source_refs": []}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}